----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Program Author: Shakil Muhammad (101259661)

Purpose: A simple simulation of Timmy and Harolds escape from dragons hollow. 
Both heroes start from [MAX_ROW-1][0] and make their way rigth-wrd from the entrance 
to the exit, avoiding downward moving birds. If a hero and a bird collide, the hero dies.
All avatar movements are randomly generated.

Header Files:
<stdio.h>
<stdlib.h>
<unistd.h>
<time.h>

Source Files:
a1-Shakil.c

Compilation Command: gcc -Wall -o a1 a1-Shakil.c

Launching instructions: No user input or interaction is required, simply start 
the program using: ./a1 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

